                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1051" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0144</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9148 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国国航的租赁业务分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Analysis on lease business in Air China</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连海事大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国航空集团公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务分析；融资租赁；经营租赁；资产负债率</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">financial analysis; financing lease; operating lease; total debt ratio</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自2002年以来，中国航空业正在经历着一个高速发展的时期，油价稳定的天时、中国市场的地利、政策鼎力支持的人和打造了一个不一样的中国航空业。政府明智的选择了两到三家大型航空公司的寡头垄断方式来保障行业健康发展。而中国国航是资本最多，国际航线最多的航空公司，它代表着中国航空在国际上的形象，是确定的民航强国的载体。其具备资源、网络、管理、市场、品牌和战略优势；通过货运业务、维修业务的相关多元化规避周期波动，将成为价值型公司的先导者。因此，如何配合公司的多元化策略，对资金的使用和资本的运作则显得更为关键。而航空业的特殊属性又注定了只有成为具备较大规模的承运人才能真正实现盈利上的最优规模，因此航空公司运营需要大量的资金。近年来，国航公司大量的飞机均通过租赁进行，本案例通过对其租赁业务进行分析，帮助学员了解经营租赁和融资租赁相关理论，以及租赁形式的选择如何影响中国国航的负债及利润情况，如何才能准确评估其真实负债水平。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China’s aviation industry is experiencing a rapid growth as a diversified unique one since 2002, with stabilized oil price, development of Chinese market and full support from central government. The central government wisely selects two to three giant airline companies as monopoly to ensure the industry grows healthy. Air China is the one with most capital as well as international routines among peers, who is not only the representative of China’s aviation industry globally but also the determined milestone. The related diversification business of Air China, e.g. freight business, maintenance business, to avoid industry periodic fluctuation, also it has huge advantages, e.g. resources, network, management, market, brand and strategy, to ensure Air China become the leading example for embedded value company. Therefore, efficiently use of fund and capital operation to comply with the company’s diversified strategy is the key factor for the aviation industry. The aviation industry’ nature deems only large-scaled carrier will be benefited from the optimized size of business, which means the airline company’s operation requires loads of cash flow. Air China rent airplanes through the lease agreement to operate, and that becomes the case study in this paper to help us understand the theory of operating lease and financing lease. Also this case will be useful to know the impact from lease formation to Air China’s liabilities and profit status, and the way of evaluating its real debt levels.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">-</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资租赁；经营租赁；会计处理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
